h2 Sign In
p Welcome to the TransCAD Cloud. Please enter your user name and password in order to manage your cloud machines.

.validation-summary-errors
  span {{validation_summary_errors}}
form
  .form-group.row
    .col-md-4
      input.form-control(placeholder='Username', ng-model='userName')
  .form-group.row
    .col-md-4
      input.form-control(type='password', placeholder='Password', ng-model='password')
  button.btn.btn-primary(ng-click="signin(userName, password)") Sign In

